{"tid":1705662,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔想見到香港人今日仲繼續淘寶","createTime":"2019-11-11T02:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T03:03:03.000Z","uid":26931,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d703c122c33ee0e43af80e5d9f762853de26181e","tid":1705662,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:16:17.000Z","msg":"今日又有手足為我地而中槍，每單新聞都令我地嬲到極致，但係新聞見到雙11淘寶又破紀錄，我好肯定當中有唔少係香港人貢獻既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好想大家唔好咁冇骨氣，為左平一百幾十蚊就屈服，諗番我地既手足同而家既心情，如果未買既，我請你地唔好買，買左既我希望你地可以退款，我地唔係唔用大陸野會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：以前都成日淘寶搵平野，但運動開始以黎冇再淘過，至少我心安理得"},{"pid":"083bf2eb36aa8d1da18df88f5d5ad18d5a114dc0","tid":1705662,"uid":262480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:18:17.000Z","msg":"公司大撚把垃圾女同事淘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26661d51948ab974c17ca6f374b6c0ce53aa9ad","tid":1705662,"uid":26931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:18:26.000Z","msg":"push，就算比你今日慳到幾百又如何，你良心過唔過意得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b803fe3b6ecddc313a050af26c635a8060c4f8","tid":1705662,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:21:19.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe743d6c313299eec569214e3b5662a5ede1ba1","tid":1705662,"uid":318916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"083bf2eb36aa8d1da18df88f5d5ad18d5a114dc0","tid":1705662,"uid":262480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:18:17.000Z","msg":"公司大撚把垃圾女同事淘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"拉去屌啦仲等"},{"pid":"3903d1628216135ff9c184c2f4ecf0ac09669c0b","tid":1705662,"uid":262480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbe743d6c3